            .</p>
               <p>TIMOTHY M'CARTY sworn.</p>
               <p>I was a seaman on board the Vigilant, letter of marque, under Captain 
               <persName id="t17870711-89-person774">
                  George
                   Barnwell
               <interp inst="t17870711-89-person774" type="surname" value="Barnwell"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-89-person774" type="given" value="George"></interp>
