                  </persName>
            ; I told him to call again; in consequence of which he did call again, but what passed between Mr. Waddington and him I cannot say; he asked me if thore was any prize money due to 
               <persName id="t17870711-89-person785">
                  James
                   Gibson
               <interp inst="t17870711-89-person785" type="surname" value="Gibson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-89-person785" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-89-person785" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Did he tell you that he had received a letter which informed him that there was a 
               <persName id="t17870711-89-person786">
                  James
                   Gibson
               <interp inst="t17870711-89-person786" type="surname" value="Gibson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-89-person786" type="given" value="James"></interp>
